OL,6,FChair of the Culture, Media and Sport
OL,7,FSelect Committee, Caroline Dinenage
OL,8,FMP, told ITV News that while the
OL,9,Ftelevision industry has seen "some
OL,10,Fprogress" in recent years, the sector
OL,11,Fhas "become synonymous with power
OL,12,Fimbalances, where a handful of
OL,13,Findividuals hold massive, in some
OL,14,Fcases, career-ending power."
